<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Instagram Post Preview</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400..900;1,400..900&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:ital,wght@0,200..800;1,200..800&display=swap');

        /* Setup 1:1 Square Aspect Ratio for Instagram */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
        }

        .instagram-post {
            width: 1080px;
            height: 1080px;
            background-color: #FAF8F5; /* Warm, calming off-white */
            box-sizing: border-box;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 90px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Top Branding */
        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .brand {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #3E3835;
        }

        .location {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #8C827D;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        /* Main Typography Block */
        .content-main {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin-top: -40px;
        }

        .tagline {
            font-size: 22px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            color: #C05A46; /* Soft cherry red tone */
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 64px;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 1.2;
            color: #24201F;
            margin: 0 0 30px 0;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 28px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #5C534E;
            margin: 0;
        }

        /* Interactive Visual Element (Mock Interface Peek) */
        .ui-preview {
            background: #FFFFFF;
            border: 1px solid #EAE5E0;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(62, 56, 53, 0.04);
            display: flex;
            gap: 40px;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .cherry-dot {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background-color: #A33B26;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 36px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(163, 59, 38, 0.2);
        }

        .ui-text h2 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 32px;
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
            color: #24201F;
        }

        .ui-text p {
            font-size: 22px;
            color: #7A706A;
        }

        /* Bottom Footer */
        .footer {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #EAE5E0;
            padding-top: 40px;
        }

        .project-name {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #3E3835;
        }

        .cta {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            color: #24201F;
            background: #EAE5E0;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- 1080x1080 Square Container -->
    <div class="instagram-post">
        
        <div class="header">
            <span class="brand">Buna Library</span>
            <span class="location">Kerala, India</span>
        </div>

        <div class="content-main">
            <div class="tagline">Coffee Science, Uncomplicated</div>
            <h1>Understand the coffee cherry without the stress.</h1>
            <p>A calm, visual exploration of ripeness, mucilage, and fermentation. Designed for curious minds who want to skip the technical jargon and simply explore.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="ui-preview">
            <div class="cherry-dot">🍒</div>
            <div class="ui-text">
                <h2>Coffee Cherry Project</h2>
                <p>An open landscape archive tracking the fruit and its traces.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <span class="project-name">by Koffy Kraft</span>
            <span class="cta">Link in Bio →</span>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
